trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> or an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref>, specifying the individual MIME formats for the parts of the HTTP transmission.
For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref> class.

Gets the collection of extensibility elements added to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref> to specify the MIME format for the parts of the MIME message.

A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref> representing extensibility elements added to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref>.
